    {
      "id": "48",
      "name": "Skills",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Normal Attack</span></p><p>Deals 2 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Physical DMG</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2025/03/27/35428890/241eba6e4c00020975cf91170050f435_2091778260687030719.png",
                "key": "Cragbiter",
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "geo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_imgs": [],
                "title": "Cragbiter"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Skill</span></p><p>Attach <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Turbo Twirly</span> to self, enter <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Nightsoul's Blessing</span>, and then gain 2 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">\"Nightsoul points.\"</span> (This skill cannot be used after the character enters <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Nightsoul's Blessing</span>)</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Nightsoul's Blessing</span></strong><br><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Nightsoul State</span><br>The character to which this is attached accumulates <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">\"Nightsoul points.\"</span> (Max 2 points)</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2025/03/27/35428890/679155be49bf5115d9f0e9b0714245b6_513793406181527421.png",
                "key": "Go, Go Turbo Twirly!",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "geo"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "talent_imgs": [],
                "title": "Go, Go Turbo Twirly!"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Burst</span></p><p>Deal 3 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">Geo DMG</span> and create 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Turbo Drill Field</span>.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Turbo Drill Field</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Combat Status</span><br>Your <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Turbo Twirly</span> deals <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">Geo DMG</span> +1, and deals <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Piercing DMG</span> +1.<br><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Usage(s): 3</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2025/03/27/35428890/bfcb025e474ce3c122399c651f56cd21_637551000041260827.png",
                "key": "Time to Get Serious! ",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "geo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "talent_imgs": [],
                "title": "Time to Get Serious! "
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Equipment Card</span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">When the character to which this is attached is switched out: </span>Consume 1 Nightsoul point, and summon 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Turbo Twirly: Let It Rip</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2025/03/27/35428890/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_3986515415689030920.png",
                "key": "Turbo Twirly",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "talent_imgs": [
                  {
                    "description": "",
                    "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2025/03/27/35428890/742121293e983249eb55fd8aa71c2ebe_5960316371409129177.png"
                  }
                ],
                "title": "Turbo Twirly"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Summon</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">End Phase:</span> Deal 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">Geo DMG</span>, deal 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Piercing DMG</span> to the next opposing character on standby.<br><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Usage(s): 1</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2025/03/27/35428890/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_4895859112192139780.png",
                "key": "Turbo Twirly: Let It Rip",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "talent_imgs": [
                  {
                    "description": "",
                    "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2025/03/27/35428890/742121293e983249eb55fd8aa71c2ebe_1339139842296766312.png"
                  }
                ],
                "title": "Turbo Twirly: Let It Rip"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>Reacts with Elements if they are already applied:<br>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">Geo</span> + <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Cryo Crystallize</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, your active character gains 1 Shield point (Can stack, max 2 points)<br>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">Geo</span> + <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Hydro Crystallize</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, your active character gains 1 Shield point (Can stack, max 2 points)<br>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">Geo</span> + <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Pyro Crystallize</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, your active character gains 1 Shield point (Can stack, max 2 points)<br>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">Geo</span> + <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Electro Crystallize</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, your active character gains 1 Shield point (Can stack, max 2 points)</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2025/03/27/35428890/fd37cbfdd3b1b2c16e6e83fb0aa96889_5255372787341911161.png",
                "key": "Geo DMG",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "talent_imgs": [],
                "title": "Geo DMG"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Physical DMG</span></strong><br>Physical DMG will not apply any Elements, nor can it engage in Elemental Reactions.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Piercing DMG</span></strong><br>Piercing DMG cannot be increased by any bonuses, but cannot be defended against using Shields or DMG Immunity either.<br></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Usage(s)</span></strong><br>After this card's effect is triggered, 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usage</span> of it will be consumed.<br>This card will be discarded immediately once it has 0 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usages</span> remaining.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2025/03/27/35428890/245c229cf6f7364c7c9a7aea3db1a1ad_1529687217605572166.png",
                "key": "Detailed Rules",
                "materials": [],
